---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Interviews - Advocacy-Led Growth"
  description="Conversations with practitioners who are running ALG - some without knowing they had a name for it."
  activeNav="interviews"
>

  <div class="section animate-in">
    <div class="section-label"><span class="num">&bull;</span> Interviews</div>
    <h1 class="t-heading-1" style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-5);">Practitioner Interviews</h1>

    <p class="section-body mb-8">
      Conversations with people who are already running advocacy-led growth - some without
      knowing they had a name for it. If you recognize your own work in the ALG framework, we'd like
      to talk.
    </p>

    <div class="notation-block">
      <span class="notation-label">Coming soon</span>
      <div>
        The interview series launches alongside ALG's first practitioner cohort. Each interview follows
        the same structure: what the practitioner does, why it works, and the moment they realized it
        maps to ALG.
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="section-body mt-8">
      Interested in being featured? Reach out to <a href="https://twitter.com/doubts" style="color: var(--accent);">@doubts</a> on X.
    </p>
  </div>

</Base>
